Predictive analytics is a category of data analytics aimed at making predictions about future outcomes based on historical data and analytics techniques such as statistical modeling and machine learning. Predictive analytics is used in various domains including finance, healthcare, marketing, retail, and travel. AI tools for predictive analytics include IBM SPSS Modeler, SAS Advanced Analytics, Oracle Data Mining, RapidMiner Studio, KNIME Analytics Platform, Alteryx Analytics, DataRobot, Microsoft Azure Machine Learning, Google Cloud AutoML, and Amazon SageMaker.
